com.antigenomics.alisa.algebra

Interface ImmutableLinearSpaceObject<O extends ImmutableLinearSpaceObject<O>>

  • Type Parameters:
    O - linear space object type
    All Superinterfaces:
    Encoding
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    LinearSpaceObject<O>, MatrixRepresentation<V,M>, VectorEncoding<V,M>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DenseMatrix, DenseTriangularMatrix, DenseVector, LinearSpaceObjectArray, Matrix, SparseMatrix, SparseTriangularMatrix, SparseVector, Vector

    public interface ImmutableLinearSpaceObject<O extends ImmutableLinearSpaceObject<O>>
extends Encoding
    A linear space object that supports addition and scaling, and has a norm. Addition and scaling operations should map to a linear space object of the same type.
